title: HGB Roadtrip 2017 - Finale
itunes:title: HGB Roadtrip 2017 - Finale
description: This is the final episode of Roadtrip 2017. Diane and Denise wrap-up talking about their last tours in New Orleans, which includes a ghost tour, and sharing a bit about the Acadian culture.
